summary: There are at least 1,000 theories circulating the internet right now speculating what TS7 will be about, what clues Taylor has...
body:
There are at least 1,000 theories circulating the internet right now speculating what TS7 will be about, what clues Taylor has already shown that we may have overlooked, or when a single will be released, etc. While some of them may be true, what I am looking forward to is what I found in the meaning of a plan tree. Victory, PEACE, and triumph…

Before/during the Rep era, she was betrayed by many people which lead to her walls being put up. But she’s letting them down again because she was/is/will ALWAYS come out on top. You know why? It is because she is a strong, beautiful, gracious soul. She is one of the few GENUINE artists left. People can cheat, bash other people and lie their way to the top but when you’re doing it from the HEART, you will always win. Taylor is undeniably one of the most talented artists of my whole existence and she deserves to be happy. She deserves peace. She deserves to be unapologetically herself.

TS7 will be a masterpiece, just like every album of hers, but I am ready for something that even the haters can’t deny. If anyone can do that, it is our girl Taylor Swift.

We’ll always stand with you.

I love you, Tay
